name: Allison Joy Ball
tweet: I’m glad to see SB 205 is one step closer to becoming law. Energy producers contribute greatly to the  Kentucky economy by providing jobs for Kentuckians and lower prices for consumers. I applaud the Senate for protecting this signature industry.

name: Allison Joy Ball
